ander of the [[Second Army (Ottoman Empire)|Second Army]]|years=March \u2013 July 1917}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Fevzi \u00c7akmak]]}}\n{{s-brk}}\n{{s-bef|before=Unknown}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Commander of the [[Seventh Army (Ottoman Empire)|Seventh Army]]|years=July \u2013 October 1917}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Fevzi \u00c7akmak]]}}\n{{s-brk}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Fevzi \u00c7akmak]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Commander of the [[Seventh Army (Ottoman Empire)|Seventh Army]]|years=August \u2013 September 1918}}\n{{s-non|reason=[[Battle of Megiddo (1918)#Destruction of the Turkish Seventh Army|Formation destroyed]]}}\n{{s-brk}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Otto Liman von Sanders]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Commander of [[Yildirim Army Group (Ottoman Empire)|Thunder Army Group]]<br />{{small|Residual elements}}|years=October \u2013 November 1918}}\n{{s-non|reason=Formation dissolved}}\n{{s-brk}}\n{{s-off}}\n{{s-brk}}\n{{s-new|reason=State founded}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of Prime Ministers of Turkey|Prime Minister of Turkey]]|years=25 April 1920 \u2013 24 January 1921}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Fevzi \u00c7akmak]]}}\n{{s-brk}}\n{{s-new|reason=State founded}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of Speakers of the Parliament of Turkey|Speaker of the Parliament of Turkey]]|years=24 April 1920 \u2013 29 October 1923}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Ali Fethi Okyar]]}}\n{{s-brk}}\n{{s-new|reason=State founded}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of Presidents of Turkey|President of Turkey]]|years=29 October 1923 \u2013 10 November 1938}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[\u0130smet \u0130n\u00f6n\u00fc]]}}\n{{s-brk}}\n{{s-ppo}}\n{{s-brk}}\n{{s-new|reason=State founded}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Republican People's Party (Turkey)|Leader of the Republican People's Party]]|years=9 September 1923 \u2013 10 November 1938}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[\u0130smet \u0130n\u00f6n\u00fc]]}}\n{{s-end}}}}\n{{Presidents of Turkey}}\n{{Prime Ministers of Turkey}}\n{{Speakers of the Parliament of Turkey}}\n{{CHP Leaders}}\n{{Turkish nationalism}}\n{{Secularism in Turkey}}\n{{Turkey topics}}\n{{Party Leaders in Turkey}}}}\n{{